	<span style="color:#E53333;">EUCJIC</span><br />
<span style="color:#E53333;">EU-China Joint Innovation Center<br />
</span>Based on the comprehensive strategic partnership between China and Europe and the impending of&nbsp; the innovation and technology cooperation,&nbsp; EU-China Joint Innovation Center has established with the support from EU-China Friendship Group in European Parliament and the EU-China Economic and Cultural Commission (EUCNC) in the ear of global innovation and rapid development of science and technology. EU-China Friendship Group aims to promote EU-China relations and cooperation within European Parliament. The current 45 members come from 20 European countries, seven major parliamentarians, 13 of whom are party heads, Parliamentary committees, delegation leaders and other important positions in the European Parliament which have great influence.Aiming to promote the economic cooperation and cultural exchange between EU countries and Chinese government， EUCNC is dedicated to promoting the EU-China cooperation in economy, culture, trade, technology and other fields and establishing an open, equal and beneficial platform for economic and cultural exchange.<br />
As the significant agency and frontline of innovation and cooperation in Europe and China, the EUCJIC is committed to the integration of Euro-China technology, joint innovation and joint venture start-up. Aim to integrate international innovative resources channels from different fields including academic, business, scientific research institutions, finance, and innovative service providers etc. To build up a comprehensive platform for EU-China innovation resources hub, exchange and cooperation channels, financial support, professional innovation services. To provide a fair and efficient supply and demand market services with advanced models and solutions. With the advantage of abundant resources from EU and China, EUCJIC actively participated in many China-EU Countries and non-EU Countries’ projects. In the new normal, EUCJIC will unceasingly contribute with new concepts, new impetus and new service to meet the EU-China Innovation development needs.
