<p align="left">
	<span style="color:#E53333;">&gt; Industrial sub centers with full coverage of every industries</span><br />
EUCJIC has setup industrial sub centers with full coverage of almost every industries, including Industry, Agriculture, Ecology, Energy, IT, Intelligent Industry, Mining, Construction, Logistics, Education, Health Care, and Finance.<br />
<img alt="" src="/data/upload/image/201704/3e2ddcac6ce13fc0b7639afb129fb0cd.png" /><br />
<span style="color:#E53333;">&gt; Regional Services Center System</span><br />
By establishing different levels of&nbsp;regional services center with different levels in European countries and China, EUCJIC is aiming to improve its regional services ability, and regional efficiency and capacity on international scientific synchronization, joint innovation and joint venture startup, gather scientific and innovation resources such as projects, industries, capital, and talents and then effectively strengthen regional international joint innovation capacities and properties.&nbsp; The network constituted by each separated regional service center forms part of global open collaborative innovation network and becomes the focus of EU-China joint innovation exchange and cooperation and an influential international scientific service platform.
