	Lead by a professional team made of entrepreneurs from many countries, including bankers, investors &amp; consultants, with over 30 years of trading experience in the industry, EUCJIF is dedicated to working with universities, science parks, research institutions, investment companies, global consulting firms and EU China Fund&nbsp; to give innovation enterprise capital support and portfolio investment and to create domestic value by introducing global technology, experts and products to China.<br />
<span style="color:#E53333;">&gt; Innovation Fund</span><br />
Strengthening the financial concern and support for enterprise innovation activities, focusing on supporting innovation projects between Europe and China, in particular to alleviate the capital pressure of SMEs in innovation and to establish investment and financing tools and support systems for innovation needs.<br />
<span style="color:#E53333;">&gt; VC Fund</span><br />
Investing in highly potential and fast growing enterprises; Focusing on outstanding joint venture start-up projects both in Europe and China; Operating VC fund in a whole new mode to promote European and Chinese enterprises to work together and then achieve common progress; Building a comprehensive and professional service platform for entrepreneurial internationalization through providing capital fund and international resources network.<br />
<span style="color:#E53333;">&gt; M&amp;A Fund</span><br />
EUCJIF is dedicated to setup an equity-typed international technology buyout fund&nbsp; to acquire technologies or technology-owned enterprises for the permission of targeted technologies and to acquire IP rights of international advanced technologies used for enterprises' extraordinary development of technological innovation&nbsp; and independence innovation capability formation and promotion.<br />
<span style="color:#E53333;">&gt; Industrial fund</span><br />
- Technology Incubation<br />
By working with international science parks, incubators and other innovation resources, EUCJIF provides improved incubation environments, including incubation bases and shared services, and sound soft service system to accelerate comprehensive development of the incubation projects for excellent technology R&amp;D teams and enterprises.<br />
- Technology Industrialization<br />
Based on market demand, EUCJIF mainly focuses on prospective and breakthrough technology achievements that would promote emerging industries of strategic importance. By cooperating with all types of financial institutions and science parks, EUCJIF is aiming to establish a professional platform for accelerating the transformation and industrialization of outstanding innovation technology achievements.
</p>
